{"tid":2400854,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳尊參加同學會！太凍齡網笑，同框合照如「兩個世代」","createTime":"2021-02-09T09:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T09:31:02.000Z","uid":318316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c7e60ffe6f083c3935fcf31ad86c6666f0a5c1","tid":2400854,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/content/84/101184/5e6d511132a4ed6020db27cef82a8ce7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcontent%2F84%2F101184%2F5e6d511132a4ed6020db27cef82a8ce7.jpg&h=b52e7689&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n吳尊在微博PO出參加同學會的照片，開心寫下：「今年的新春聚會，我終於沒飛了！這些年大家的變化太大了，奇妙的是大家的感覺還是跟30年前一樣&hellip;&hellip;他們幫我勾起了太多的回憶，也一直爆我的料！」勾起不少粉絲好奇他被爆了什麼料，吳尊則笑著自首頑皮，常常作弄女同學。<br />\n<br />\n而照片一PO出，明明吳尊和同學們都是40歲出頭，但明顯可見勤於健身的吳尊，不論皮膚、身材都特別年輕，在大合照中成為亮點，引來不少網友留言笑「這是同齡人？有種去見長輩的感覺」、「活生生把老同學比成了兩個時代的人」、「這是把同學熬成了爹吧哈哈哈」、「你是學弟對吧」、「就你吃了防腐劑」、「你還是當年那個同學沒有改變吧」，甚至衝上微博熱搜榜，掀起熱議。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2021-02-07/1024/20210207003915.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2021-02-07%2F1024%2F20210207003915.jpg%20&h=fb65ba8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ctwant.com/images/cover/84/101184/md-a072538daad467ea8f5084de5a78c1fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ctwant.com%2Fimages%2Fcover%2F84%2F101184%2Fmd-a072538daad467ea8f5084de5a78c1fc.jpg&h=87d6f714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210207003883-260404?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210207003883-260404%3Fchdtv&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b2d2c6f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210207003883-260404?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"29a6a12226fb16cf538fcf858c8952de934dedc5","tid":2400854,"uid":101812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:25:37.000Z","msg":"班同學似佢老豆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa9880c36334eb890ab5f05106b70cf6b320f34","tid":2400854,"uid":80047,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁屈機"},{"pid":"d1a741b17e221e46714531380436f60592dcefaf","tid":2400854,"uid":260201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"你玩晒啦"}]}